<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hap2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hap,</orth> vb. to happen, to chance, to come to pass: <cit><quote>if thou issueless shalt h. to die,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 9.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 9, 3</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if it so h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 1, 28</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.4.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 4, 108</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.2.60" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 2, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.88" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.3.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 3, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.249" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 249</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.6.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 6, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.1.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 1, 127</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.0." default="NO" valid="yes">II Prol. 22</bibl>.
